trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of deployment to be performed on a file.
trans-unit.target: 指定要对文件执行的部署类型。

trans-unit.source: Specifies deployment of the file as an Application Global Resource to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定作为应用程序全局资源部署到 SharePoint 的文件部署。

trans-unit.source: The default path for AppGlobalResource is: <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\App_GlobalResources</c>.
trans-unit.target: AppGlobalResource 的默认路径为 <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\App_GlobalResources</c>。

trans-unit.source: Application Global Resources are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 应用程序全局资源引用的包清单 (manifest.xml)。

trans-unit.source: They are deployed to the 'App_GlobalResources' folder of the SharePoint Web application.
trans-unit.target: 它们将部署到 SharePoint Web 应用程序的 App_GlobalResources 文件夹。

trans-unit.source: Specifies deployment of the file as an Application Resource to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定作为应用程序资源部署到 SharePoint 的文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Application Resources are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 应用程序资源由包清单 (manifest.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for ApplicationResource is: <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\Resources</c>.
trans-unit.target: ApplicationResource 的默认路径为 <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\Resources</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies deployment of the file as part of an app for SharePoint, but not packaged into a wsp.
trans-unit.target: 指定作为 SharePoint 的应用的一部分、但未打包到 wsp 的文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Specifies deployment of the file as a Class Resource to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定作为类资源部署到 SharePoint 的文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Class Resources are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 类资源由包清单 (manifest.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for ClassResource is <c>{ClassResourcePath}</c>.
trans-unit.target: ClassResource 的默认路径为 <c>{ClassResourcePath}</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies a file marked as Resource that is referenced in the package manifest as a Dwp file.
trans-unit.target: 指定一个标记为“资源”的文件，该资源在包清单中作为 Dwp 文件被引用。

trans-unit.source: Dwp files are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: Dwp 文件由包清单 (manifest.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for DwpFile is <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\wpcatalog</c>.
trans-unit.target: DwpFile 的默认路径为 <c>{WebApplicationRoot}\wpcatalog</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the deployment of element files to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定部署到 SharePoint 的元素文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Element files are referenced by the feature manifest (feature.xml).
trans-unit.target: 元素文件由功能清单 (feature.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for ElementFile is <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>.
trans-unit.target: ElementFile 的默认路径为 <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the deployment of element manifests to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定部署到 SharePoint 的元素清单部署。

trans-unit.source: Element manifests are referenced by the feature manifest (feature.xml).
trans-unit.target: 元素清单由功能清单 (feature.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for ElementManifest is <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>.
trans-unit.target: ElementManifest 的默认路径为 <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies files that are not deployed to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定不部署到 SharePoint 的文件。

trans-unit.source: The default path for NoDeployment is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: NoDeployment 的默认路径为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Specifies files marked as Package Only, which are included in the WSP file without any deployment details.
trans-unit.target: 指定标记为“仅限包”的文件，该文件包含在 WSP 文件中，且无任何部署详细信息。

trans-unit.source: The default path for PackageOnly is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: PackageOnly 的默认路径为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Specifies deployment of the file as Resource file to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定作为资源文件部署到 SharePoint 的文件部署。

trans-unit.source: The default path for Resource is <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>.
trans-unit.target: Resource 的默认路径为 <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template\Features</c>。

trans-unit.source: Resource files are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 资源文件引用的包清单 (manifest.xml)。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the deployment of root files to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定部署到 SharePoint 的根文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Root files are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 根文件由包清单 (manifest.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for RootFile is <c>{SharePointRoot}</c>.
trans-unit.target: RootFile 的默认路径为 <c>{SharePointRoot}</c>。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the deployment of template files to SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 指定部署到 SharePoint 的模板文件部署。

trans-unit.source: Template files are referenced by the package manifest (manifest.xml).
trans-unit.target: 模板文件由包清单 (manifest.xml) 引用。

trans-unit.source: The default path for TemplateFile is <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template</c>.
trans-unit.target: TemplateFile 的默认路径为 <c>{SharePointRoot}\Template</c>。
